      </button>
    </h2>
    <div id="ongoing" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#accordionWorks">
      <div class="accordion-body">
        <strong> Some of my works in progress are listed below, and the most mature come along with some preprints.</strong> <br>
        I welcome (m)any discussions about those topics, and you are welcome to contact me to exchange about them.

         <ul>
            <li> <i> Chord diagrams of loops in surfaces 1 : split decompositions of their interlace graphs </i>
            </li>
            
            <li> <i> Chord diagrams of loops in surfaces 2 : smoothing posets, hopf algebra, and polynomial invariants </i>
            </li>
            
            <li> <i> Chord diagrams of loops in surfaces 3 : isotopy classes of hyperbolic geodesics </i>
            </li>
            
            <li> <i> Linking numbers of modular knots and scalar products of modular forms </i>
            </li>
            
            <li> <i> Representations of the adelic modular group : equidistribution of structure coefficients and periods of automorphic forms </i>
            </li> 
            
            <li> <i> Gauss linking forms for hyperbolic geodesics </i>
            </li>
            
            <li> <i> Mapping class groups of mapping tori </i>
            </li>
            
            <li> <i> Surgery distances between 3-manifolds </i>
            </li>
         </ul>
